datasets.name: b3e86a40
datasets.query:
with eval_log as (
    select 
        *,
        case
            when `response/overall_assessment/rating` = "yes" then "no_quality_issue"
            when `response/overall_assessment/rating` = "no" then "has_quality_issue"
            else null
        end as overall_assessment,
        execution_duration_ms / 1000 as execution_time_s,
        concat(
            '/ml/experiments/',
            experiment_id,
            '/runs/',
            run_id,
            '/evaluations?searchQuery=',
            databricks_request_id
        ) as eval_details
    from {{eval_requests_log_table_name}}
    where 
        run_id is not null 
        and run_id != "skipped"
)
select eval_log.*
from eval_log

datasets.name: f31542f7
datasets.query:
with eval_log as (
    select 
        *,
        case
            when `response/overall_assessment/rating` = "yes" then "no_quality_issue"
            when `response/overall_assessment/rating` = "no" then "has_quality_issue"
            else null
        end as overall_assessment,
        execution_duration_ms / 1000 as execution_time_s,
        case 
            when run_id is not null and run_id != "skipped" then concat(
                '/ml/experiments/',
                experiment_id,
                '/runs/',
                run_id,
                '/evaluations?searchQuery=',
                databricks_request_id
            )
            else null
        end as eval_details
    from {{eval_requests_log_table_name}}
)
select
    eval_log.*
from eval_log
